## A* Path Planning Algorithm

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Start Node] --> B{Goal Reached?}
    B -->|No| C[Select Node with lowest f = g + h]
    C --> D[Generate Neighbors]
    D --> E[Calculate g, h, f values]
    E --> F{Neighbor in Open/Closed List?}
    F -->|No| G[Add to Open List]
    F -->|Yes| H{Better Path Found?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Update Path]
    H -->|No| J[Continue]
    G --> B
    I --> B
    J --> B
    B -->|Yes| K[Reconstruct Path]

    style A fill:#ffcccc
    style K fill:#ccffcc
```